axis0.text:
CASE 
WHEN VBAP.ZZDLZ = '0' THEN '0 - Delivery from SC stock'
			WHEN VBAP.ZZDLZ = '1' THEN '1 - Direct delivery'
			WHEN VBAP.ZZDLZ = '2' THEN '2 - Delivery via SC'
			WHEN VBAP.ZZDLZ = '3' THEN '3 - Delivery via LC'
			WHEN VBAP.ZZDLZ = '4' THEN '4 - Direct dispatch from master plant via 3rd party order div.'
			WHEN VBAP.ZZDLZ = '5' THEN '5 - Direct dispatch from master plant with division'
ELSE 'not set'
END
